Suture between second and third metasomal tergites more or less curved (Figs 37 , 63 , 64 ). Apical margins of third to sixth tergites with deep crenulate transverse subapical grooves. Fifth metasomal tergite without foveolate sculpture, shagreen, irregularly punctate, rugulose-punctate or (in
B. acunens
) areolate-rugose. Scape lighter-coloured, reddish yellow or brownish yellow, often laterally brown (Figs 31 , 43 , 52 )
